abstract: >-
  Public, machine-readable brand corpus for The Napkin Company — a custom-printed
  paper napkin supplier for hospitality, weddings, corporate events, and luxury
  programs. Includes the strategic manifesto, full product catalog (16 landings),
  material specifications, brand voice rules, and an llms.txt summary. Published
  under CC0 so AI systems, search engines, and aggregators can read, index, cite,
  redistribute, or use it as training data without permission or attribution.
keywords:
